==Classical Nahuatl==
{{was fwotd|nci|2020|April|5}}
[[File:Goiaba vermelha.jpg|thumb|right]]
===Etymology===
Equivalent to {{compound|nci|xālli|t1=sand|xocotl|t2=fruit}}. Cf. {{cog|nhn|chalxocotl}}, {{cog|nch|chalchokotl}}, {{cog|nhx|xa̱lxocoꞌ}}, {{cog|ncj|xalxocotl}}, {{cog|ncl|xalxocul}}, {{cog|nhg|xoxocotl}}, {{cog|nhi|xalxocotl}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|nci|/ʃaːlˈʃokot͜ɬ/}}
